    "How many children my dad has\", ChatGPT provided an incorrect response of 8.",
    "This highlights that ChatGPT can be prone to remembering things verbatim and can be quite rigidfoot_12.• The extent to which ChatGPT has commonsense and ways to enhance it are uncertain (See [19,31]).Based on our research, it appears that ChatGPT performs admirably when it comes to answering queries that involve common sense reasoning.",
    "However, further systematic evaluation is required to confirm this observation.• ChatGPT appears to be limited in its ability to generate creative solutions to novel problems, particularly those in mathematics that are still unsolved.",
    "As a test of this ability, I posed several questions to ChatGPT, including the task of proving that there are infinitely many prime numbers, which it was able to answer correctly by referencing existing solutions on the web.",
    "When I asked ChatGPT to define what a twin prime is, it provided a correct definition."
